{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Supply body suits to all to combat COVID19 and other air-transmitted viruses",
        "additional_details": "Every person must wear the suit outdoor. On return home - have a shower in the suit for 10min with lots of water and soap. Remove the suit.\r\nSuit must be - comfortable, water and air proof.\r\nElectronic device - control citizen location, temperature, if comply with advice.\r\nAdvantages:\r\n1. The physical barrier should eliminate the host - virus carrier.\r\n2. Those who do not comply - isolate by police.\r\n3. Multi-use - any future epidemic. \r\n\r\n2-3 weeks - all back to normal.",
        "background": "My approach is:\r\n1. Supply every citizen with partial (head + arms + body) or full body suit and full face cover mask with air-filters.\r\n2. Each suit must come with smart-watch like device to control: a). Integrity of the suit; b). Location - indoor or outdoor; c). Temperature.\r\n3. Wear for 3 weeks.",
